        <h2>Accessing Shortcut Menus on PC and Mac</h2>
        <p>You can access shortcut menus by right-clicking on both PC and Mac if you are using a two button mouse.  If you are working on a Mac with a one-button mouse, use CTRL-click to access the shortcut menu. This guide uses the term right-click.</p>
